# LAMMPS input file generated by NPGrowth
# This file is intended to be modified by the user
# For example things that needs to be updated are the pair_coeff
# and mass command when using different atoms elements.
# The basic example expect a Cu_u3.eam potential file inside potentials folder

### Initialize #################################
units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary f f f

### System definition ##########################
region simulation_box block -500 50 -50 50 -50 50
create_box 1 simulation_box
labelmap atom 1 Cu
read_dump seeds/Cu_cube.xyz 0 x y z box no add yes format xyz

### Logic for atom groups #######################
group added empty
group initial subtract all added
compute coordination added coord/atom cutoff 4.9 group initial
variable attached atom "c_coordination > 2"
group attached dynamic added var attached every 2

### Settings ###################################
pair_style eam
pair_coeff * * potentials/Cu_u3.eam
mass 1 63.55
fix momentum_fix initial momentum 1 linear 1 1 1 angular rescale

### Visualize ###################################
thermo 50
thermo_style custom step temp pe ke etotal press
dump dump1 all custom 50 ./sample.traj id type element x y z v_attached
dump_modify dump1 element Cu

### Run #########################################
timestep 0.002
fix my_nve all nve
fix lgv_initial initial langevin 300.0 300.0 0.1 42
include deposit.in
run 20000 every 50 "group attached static" "group initial union attached initial" "group added subtract added attached" "group attached dynamic added var attached every 2"
